OL,12,     FThe Battle for the Arctic: Every
OL,13,     FAutumn, polar bears gather on the
OL,14,     Fshores of Hudson Bay in Canada to
OL,15,     Fwait for the sea ice to form so
OL,16,     Fthey can begin their winter hunt.
